                                       'brother, as I consider him, I have '
                                       'written to you briefly, exhorting, and '
                                       'testifying that this is the true grace '
                                       'of God in which you stand.\n'
                                       'She who is in Babylon, chosen together '
                                       'with you, greets you; and so does '
                                       'Mark, my son.\n'
                                       'Greet one another with a kiss of love. '
                                       'Peace be to you all who are in Christ '
                                       'Jesus. Amen.\n',
