                                               'and of the Lord, having '
                                               'received the word in much '
                                               'affliction, with joy of the '
                                               'Holy Spirit,\n'
                                               'so that you became an example '
                                               'to all who believe in '
                                               'Macedonia and in Achaia.\n'
