                                               'the night; and those who are '
                                               'drunk are drunk in the night.\n'
                                               'But let us, since we belong to '
                                               'the day, be sober, putting on '
                                               'the breastplate of faith and '
                                               'love, and, for a helmet, the '
                                               'hope of salvation.\n'
