                                         'homosexuals, for slave-traders, for '
                                         'liars, for perjurers, and for any '
                                         'other thing contrary to the sound '
                                         'doctrine;\n'
                                         'according to the Good News of the '
                                         'glory of the blessed God, which was '
                                         'committed to my trust.\n'
