                                         'Christ Jesus our Lord, because he '
                                         'counted me faithful, appointing me '
                                         'to service;\n'
                                         'although I was before a blasphemer, '
                                         'a persecutor, and insolent. However, '
                                         'I obtained mercy, because I did it '
                                         'ignorantly in unbelief.\n'
                                         'The grace of our Lord abounded '
                                         'exceedingly with faith and love '
                                         'which is in Christ Jesus.\n'
                                         'The saying is faithful and worthy of '
                                         'all acceptance, that Christ Jesus '
                                         'came into the world to save sinners; '
                                         'of whom I am chief.\n'
