                                         'good foundation against the time to '
                                         'come, that they may lay hold of '
                                         'eternal life.\n'
                                         'Timothy, guard that which is '
                                         'committed to you, turning away from '
                                         'the empty chatter and oppositions of '
                                         'what is falsely called knowledge;\n'
                                         'which some profess, and thus have '
                                         'wandered from the faith. Grace be '
