                                             'our Father and the Lord Jesus '
                                             'Christ.\n'
                                             'Blessed be the God and Father of '
                                             'our Lord Jesus Christ, the '
                                             'Father of mercies and God of all '
                                             'comfort;\n'
                                             'who comforts us in all our '
                                             'affliction, that we may be able '
                                             'to comfort those who are in any '
                                             'affliction, through the comfort '
                                             'with which we ourselves are '
                                             'comforted by God.\n'
