                                             'to your own selves, that Jesus '
                                             "Christ is in you?'unless indeed "
                                             'you are disqualified.\n'
                                             'But I hope that you will know '
                                             "that we aren't disqualified.\n"
                                             'Now I pray to God that you do no '
