                                       'it.\n'
                                       'His appearance was like lightning, and '
                                       'his clothing white as snow.\n'
                                       'For fear of him, the guards shook, and '
                                       'became like dead men.\n'
                                       "The angel answered the women, 'Don't "
                                       'be afraid, for I know that you seek '
