                                          'voice, like a trumpet\n'
                                          'saying,\n'
                                          "'What you see, write in a book and "
                                          'send to the seven assemblies:\n'
                                          ' to Ephesus, Smyrna, Pergamum, '
                                          'Thyatira, Sardis, Philadelphia, and '
                                          "to Laodicea.'\n"
