                                          'words of the prophecy of this book, '
                                          'for the time is at hand.\n'
                                          'He who acts unjustly, let him act '
                                          'unjustly still. He who is filthy, '
                                          'let him be filthy still. He who is '
                                          'righteous, let him do righteousness '
                                          'still. He who is holy, let him be '
                                          "holy still.'\n"
                                          '\n'
