                                          'everyone who loves and practices '
                                          'falsehood.\n'
                                          '\n'
                                          '\n'
                                          'I, Jesus, have sent my angel to '
                                          'testify these things to you for the '
                                          'assemblies. I am the root and the '
                                          'offspring of David; the Bright and '
                                          "Morning Star.'\n"
                                          'The Spirit and the bride say, '
                                          "'Come!' He who hears, let him say, "
                                          "'Come!' He who is thirsty, let him "
                                          'come. He who desires, let him take '
                                          'the water of life freely.\n'
                                          'I testify to everyone who hears the '
                                          'words of the prophecy of this book, '
                                          'if anyone adds to them, may God add '
                                          'to him the plagues which are '
                                          'written in this book.\n'
                                          'If anyone takes away from the words '
