                                      'my spirit in the Good News of his Son, '
                                      'how unceasingly I make mention of you '
                                      'always in my prayers,\n'
                                      'requesting, if by any means now at last '
                                      'I may be prospered by the will of God '
                                      'to come to you.\n'
                                      'For I long to see you, that I may '
                                      'impart to you some spiritual gift, to '
                                      'the end that you may be established;\n'
