                                      "I said, 'My lord, what will be the "
                                      "outcome of these things?'\n"
                                      "He said, 'Go your way, Daniel; for the "
                                      'words are shut up and sealed until the '
                                      'time of the end.\n'
                                      'Many will purify themselves, and make '
                                      'themselves white, and be refined; but '
                                      'the wicked will do wickedly; and none '
                                      'of the wicked will understand; but '
                                      'those who are wise will understand.\n'
                                      "'From the time that the continual burnt "
                                      'offering is taken away, and the '
