                                           'Kadesh Barnea.\n'
                                           "I said to you, 'You have come to "
                                           'the hill country of the Amorites, '
                                           'which Yahweh our God gives to us.\n'
                                           'Behold, Yahweh your God has set '
                                           'the land before you. Go up, take '
                                           'possession, as Yahweh, the God of '
                                           'your fathers, has spoken to you. '
                                           "Don't be afraid, neither be "
                                           "dismayed.'\n"
