                                           'give it to them, and they shall '
                                           'possess it.\n'
                                           'But as for you, turn, and take '
                                           'your journey into the wilderness '
                                           "by the way to the Red Sea.'\n"
                                           'Then you answered and said to me, '
                                           "'We have sinned against Yahweh, we "
                                           'will go up and fight, according to '
                                           'all that Yahweh our God commanded '
                                           "us.' Every man of you put on his "
                                           'weapons of war, and presumed to go '
                                           'up into the hill country.\n'
                                           "Yahweh said to me, 'Tell them, "
                                           "'Don't go up and don't fight; for "
                                           'I am not among you; lest you be '
                                           "struck before your enemies.''\n"
                                           "So I spoke to you, and you didn't "
