                                        "north,' says Yahweh.\n"
                                        "'They will come, and they will each "
                                        'set his throne at the entrance of the '
                                        'gates of Jerusalem,\n'
                                        'and against all its walls all around, '
                                        'and against all the cities of Judah.\n'
                                        'I will utter my judgments against '
                                        'them concerning all their '
                                        'wickedness,\n'
                                        'in that they have forsaken me,\n'
                                        'and have burned incense to other '
                                        'gods,\n'
                                        'and worshiped the works of their own '
                                        'hands.\n'
                                        "'You therefore put your belt on your "
                                        'waist, arise, and say to them all '
