                                      'inhabitants of Beth Shemesh and of Beth '
                                      'Anath became subject to forced labor.\n'
                                      'The Amorites forced the children of Dan '
                                      'into the hill country, for they would '
                                      'not allow them to come down to the '
                                      'valley;\n'
                                      'but the Amorites would dwell in Mount '
