                                       'six hundred three thousand five '
                                       'hundred fifty.\n'
                                       'But the Levites after the tribe of '
                                       'their fathers were not counted among '
                                       'them.\n'
                                       'For Yahweh spoke to Moses, saying,\n'
                                       "'Only the tribe of Levi you shall not "
                                       'count, neither shall you take a census '
                                       'of them among the children of Israel;\n'
                                       'but appoint the Levites over the '
