                                       'there may be no wrath on the '
                                       'congregation of the children of '
                                       'Israel: and the Levites shall be '
                                       'responsible for the Tabernacle of the '
                                       "Testimony.'\n"
                                       'Thus the children of Israel did. '
                                       'According to all that Yahweh commanded '
                                       'Moses, so they did.\n'
                                       "The heads of the fathers' households "
                                       'of the family of the children of '
                                       'Gilead, the son of Machir, the son of '
