                                       'of Joseph, came near, and spoke before '
                                       'Moses, and before the princes, the '
                                       "heads of the fathers' households of "
                                       'the children of Israel.\n'
                                       "They said, 'Yahweh commanded my lord "
                                       'to give the land for inheritance by '
                                       'lot to the children of Israel. My lord '
