                                        "don't consent.\n"
                                        "If they say, 'Come with us.\n"
                                        "Let's lay in wait for blood.\n"
                                        "Let's lurk secretly for the innocent "
                                        'without cause.\n'
                                        "Let's swallow them up alive like "
                                        'Sheol,\n'
                                        'and whole, like those who go down '
                                        'into the pit.\n'
                                        "We'll find all valuable wealth.\n"
