                                         "Armies says: 'I am jealous for "
                                         'Jerusalem and for Zion with a great '
                                         'jealousy.\n'
                                         'I am very angry with the nations '
                                         'that are at ease; for I was but a '
                                         'little displeased, but they added to '
                                         "the calamity.'\n"
                                         "Therefore Yahweh says: 'I have "
